txt.en: 'Do not succumb to the fear of this place, my friends.'
'Come! The bridge should be further down the road.'
'The very air of this place is foul, Mithrandir. Are you certain we should come here?'
'Very well, Mithrandir. We will stand guard.'
'Fear not the evil that dwel in this valley.'
'We must not trouble ourselves with the city. We are here for the bridge alone.'
'We must not allow any servants of Mordor to come this way.'
'Stand back. This task is mine to undertake.'
'These foes will not long stand before us!'
'No denizen of Minas Morgul will cross!'
